Kat Green https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kat_Green 0 Kat Green born as Kathryn Greenblatt is an American actress, composer, producer and writer. She's best known for being the first woman to play Marvel Comics' Alicia Masters in The Fantastic Four in 1994, directed by Oley Sassone and co-produced by Roger Corman.
